{"tid":2106250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[疑似武肺師]成個政府先係攬炒之母！！！","createTime":"2020-07-13T08:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T08:36:58.000Z","uid":164491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"896d63a67a6c5681f5b3f15c48eb07433dc10843","tid":2106250,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"話說又爆左咁多　自己又去過高危地區 本著小小良心自動去做檢測<br />\n誰不知係香港呢個咁先進既城市　要去做檢測足足花左我大半日既時間！<br />\n<br />\n首先　<span class=\"red\"><strong>（我唸好多人都真係唔知）</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">個Ｄ樣本瓶唔係你話想有就有！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係你要去睇醫生　佢<strong><span class=\"x-large\">睇完覺得你有需要</span></strong>　先至會俾你<br />\n然後你再要等二日　再番去個<strong><span class=\"x-large\">指定</span></strong>診所交番！<br />\nＰＳ：　就算你有錢睇私家診所　都<ins><strong>唔係</strong></ins>間間都有樣本瓶！！！<br />\n<br />\n１。要<strong><span class=\"red\">睇左醫生先可以有樣本瓶</span></strong>呢個程序簡單係ＯＮ９至極<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係人都知　武肺唔一定有明顯病徹！！！！<br />\n同你講想做個ＴＥＳＴ　我表面無病無痛行入去<br />\n咁你係唔係唔會俾個樣本瓶我？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日袁國勇博士日日己經係度屌緊點解唔俾多Ｄ人做測試<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>想問你個程序咁撚繁複　有心做都俾你嚇到唔做啦！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n２。本來香港個醫療系統應付本身既需要己經幾乎飽和<br />\n每一日去診所睇病既人多不勝數<br />\n如果你懷疑自已有　但無明顯病徵兆　你仲要去診所等睇醫生<br />\n成個過程　<strong>你可能己經唔知接觸左幾多個人</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">醫生護士個個都有機會俾你傳染！！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n３。我想講呢　<br />\n個政府網頁話咩你可以用ＧＯＧＯＶＡＮ／ＰＩＣＫＵＰ去送樣本瓶<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">係幫你運送ＪＡ</span></strong>　<ins><span class=\"blue\">唔係提供個樣本瓶俾你做測試</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n見到香港爆到咁真係好撚心痛　又可能要無多幾條人命<br />\n明明有大把錢你唔請多Ｄ人去幫香港人做測試<br />\n哂埋Ｄ錢去整乜撚野　底褲ＣＵ　ＭＡＳＫ<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">哂左咁撚多時間　樓主我真係好撚嬲  <br />\n強烈遣責政府毫不作為！！！！<br />\n馬上提供大量樣本瓶同埋樣本收集箱俾市民自行交衛生署檢測！！！！！！<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呀爺準備好錢大爆發個陣托市未？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">ＰＳ：請推ＰＯＳＴ俾更多人知　到底而家發生緊咩事！！！！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cd4f4fda518156be85d61bdfa80053deb7f74a04","tid":2106250,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:23:38.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"ba03559279cf84625aa6d0b672ba79090df191b4","tid":2106250,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d8e73e89e0ad8f40ccfa9e66d6d4e127ea65c936","tid":2106250,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:23:59.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a26db37dc1d79f09a0879d6c6f696ad720256b90","tid":2106250,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"82316d25e8adde6d61a1ab10de2a8d806d281ea8","tid":2106250,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"c7765da25917905eafaea6a537b3a79cd1d9d0c8","tid":2106250,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"正